client.services

Interface IServer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    MockServer, ServerProxy

    public interface IServer
    This is the common interface that both the real and mock servers implement. By providing this, we can substitute the real or mock server as needed for testing.
    Author:
    Derek Argueta
